pageContext.claim: “ I went, I held a Bible in front of a church that the agitators and anarchists, they call them protesters. They tried to burn down a church. I held a Bible up in front of the church. They said it was a terrible thing I did.”
pageContext.analysis: People criticized Trump because teargas and less lethal munitions were used in order to clear protesters out of the way on short notice, allowing for the president to take the photograph.
